{"tid":1727072,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(FB轉載）原來黑警前世真係日本皇軍來","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:51:27.000Z","uid":1426,"like":75,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"53595f946b875785a9c42be4deaa7445072ea38a","tid":1727072,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQBmQ2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQBmQ2o.jpg&h=5c7a86d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDqOv2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDqOv2p.jpg&h=f7f50a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wZNUrAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwZNUrAL.jpg&h=7c157cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BbkuZVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBbkuZVM.jpg&h=50952767&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nubNMAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnubNMAM.jpg&h=e5412df0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12934ns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12934ns.jpg&h=eb2c86f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSiPZVO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSiPZVO.jpg&h=b51d95d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家信唔信有輪迴轉世？<br />\n反正我就信，<br />\n遲早俾人放多次上軍事法庭<br />\n日本皇軍一齊轉世投胎香港警察<br />\n山本汪（山本五十六），<br />\n江村sir（岡村寧次），<br />\n親愛嘅謝中將（石原莞爾）<br />\n李侵華（武藤章）<br />\n我哋嘅大波華（戶栗郁子） <br />\n麥生（児玉 誉士夫）<br />\n唔好以為除眼鏡認你唔到<br />\n光頭仔（永野修身）<br />\n原來上世係元帥，<br />\n唔怪得知林鄭都夠膽屌啦<br />\n<br />\nFrom Facebook 香港人連儂牆"},{"pid":"86924cf4792790dc96a10efd2e0f7c50d9d529d1","tid":1727072,"uid":189157,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"怪力亂神<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"5e0193d2a202bfe270299a7e32eb93f5dbe5c32a","tid":1727072,"uid":154245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"但係皇軍都冇咁過份wor"},{"pid":"00d4d6d3b2202b3bb6c0ecb446c086238fd493a0","tid":1727072,"uid":329977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"超級大核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065e55b6b79da42f7188bacb5fbd2424827da032","tid":1727072,"uid":70779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a3afe4aa5906b21e10dee240b02fa095302ec9","tid":1727072,"uid":312242,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:26:39.000Z","msg":"香港警察有咩資格做日本皇軍呀<br />\n<br />\n日本軍對著機關槍衝過去唔怕死 為咗自己國家犧牲 為咗自己屋企去做肉彈 (例如特攻隊) 即係話日本嘅自殺式攻擊<br />\n<br />\n香港警察有乜嘢資格。 自己full gear見到啲冇武器嘅市民都驚到仆街"},{"pid":"b503e5672c7ffc5c494da53a6cdba38e856fa31a","tid":1727072,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913a31438d635538c9372d519675d8bb095adb5d","tid":1727072,"uid":44019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"人人得以誅之<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e67317f0c1754a21f3c4e205ed8c2dff72908f","tid":1727072,"uid":262674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"上世食唔到香港<br />\n<br />\n今次再番黎想食左香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edf428f82119e25015faea063b7d1b7cc7bae21","tid":1727072,"uid":19476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"會唔會係後代 不推文"},{"pid":"13eaeaa226589a6317c6ea4ad8a0a3afd